Statistical report of NDgene

Report created by RAPID

30 January 2019

This report provides the basic statistical analysis of NDgene. It consists of various single category plots detailing on the distribution of read length, strand, and base modification. It also contains double category plots showing the combinations of aforementioned.

Total reads aligned to NDgene : 627

Note: If graphs under some category are absent, it means there is not sufficient data with respect to that category.
